#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:1 of
msgid "Compute the N-dimensional discrete Fourier Transform."
msgstr "计算 N 维离散傅里叶变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:3 of
msgid ""
"This function computes the *N*-dimensional discrete Fourier Transform "
"over any number of axes in an *M*-dimensional tensor by means of the Fast"
" Fourier Transform (FFT)."
msgstr ""
"此函数通过快速傅里叶变换（FFT）在 *M* 维张量中的任意数量轴上计算 *N* 维"
"离散傅里叶变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:7 of
msgid "Input tensor, can be complex."
msgstr "输入张量，可以是复数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:9 of
msgid ""
"Shape (length of each transformed axis) of the output (``s[0]`` refers to"
" axis 0, ``s[1]`` to axis 1, etc.). This corresponds to ``n`` for "
"``fft(x, n)``. Along any axis, if the given shape is smaller than that of"
" the input, the input is cropped.  If it is larger, the input is padded "
"with zeros. if `s` is not given, the shape of the input along the axes "
"specified by `axes` is used."
msgstr ""
"输出的形状（每个变换轴的长度）（``s[0]`` 指轴 0，``s[1]`` 指轴 1，等等）"
"。这对应于 ``fft(x, n)`` 中的 ``n``。在任意轴上，如果给定的形状小于输入，"
"则裁剪输入；如果大于输入，则用零填充。如果未给出 `s`，则使用输入在由 `"
"axes` 指定轴上的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:17 of
msgid ""
"Axes over which to compute the FFT.  If not given, the last ``len(s)`` "
"axes are used, or all axes if `s` is also not specified. Repeated indices"
" in `axes` means that the transform over that axis is performed multiple "
"times."
msgstr ""
"要计算 FFT 的轴。如果未给出，则使用最后 ``len(s)`` 个轴；如果也未指定 `s`"
"，则使用所有轴。在 `axes` 中重复的索引意味着在该轴上的变换将执行多次。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:22 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `mt.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `mt.fft`）。默认为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:25 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axes"
" indicated by `axes`, or by a combination of `s` and `a`, as explained in"
" the parameters section above."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 被截断或零填充的输入，沿由 `axes` 指示的轴变换，或者由 `s` 和 "
"`a` 的组合变换，如上述参数部分所述。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:30 of
msgid "If `s` and `axes` have different length."
msgstr "如果 `s` 和 `axes` 长度不同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:31 of
msgid "If an element of `axes` is larger than than the number of axes of `a`."
msgstr "如果 `axes` 的某个元素大于 `a` 的轴数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:36 of
msgid ""
"Overall view of discrete Fourier transforms, with definitions and "
"conventions used."
msgstr "离散傅里叶变换的总体视图，包含使用的定义和约定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:39 of
msgid "The inverse of `fftn`, the inverse *n*-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "`fftn` 的逆变换，即逆 *n* 维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:41 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:42 of
msgid "The one-dimensional FFT, with definitions and conventions used."
msgstr "一维 FFT，包含使用的定义和约定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:44 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rfftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:45 of
msgid "The *n*-dimensional FFT of real input."
msgstr "实数输入的 *n* 维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:47 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:48 of
msgid "The two-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "二维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:50 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fftshift`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:51 of
msgid "Shifts zero-frequency terms to centre of tensor"
msgstr "将零频率项移到张量中心"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:54 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:55 of
msgid ""
"The output, analogously to `fft`, contains the term for zero frequency in"
" the low-order corner of all axes, the positive frequency terms in the "
"first half of all axes, the term for the Nyquist frequency in the middle "
"of all axes and the negative frequency terms in the second half of all "
"axes, in order of decreasingly negative frequency."
msgstr ""
"输出类似于 `fft`，在所有轴的低阶角包含零频率项，在所有轴的前半部分包含正"
"频率项，在所有轴的中间包含奈奎斯特频率项，在所有轴的后半部分包含负频率项"
"，按频率递减顺序排列。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fftn.fftn:61 of
msgid "See `mt.fft` for details, definitions and conventions used."
msgstr "有关详细信息、定义和使用的约定，请参见 `mt.fft`。"

